# Step 1 – Create the Folder Structure

Inside the `lib` folder, create these folders:

```text
lib/
│
├── screens/
├── widgets/
├── services/
├── models/
└── utils/
```

For today, we'll only use the `screens` folder.

---

# Step 2 – Create New Files

Inside `lib/screens`, create:

```text
splash_screen.dart
login_screen.dart
```

Your project should now look like:

```text
lib/
│
├── main.dart
│
├── screens/
│      ├── splash_screen.dart
│      └── login_screen.dart
│
├── widgets/
├── services/
├── models/
└── utils/
```

