# Step 3 – Replace `main.dart`

Delete everything inside `main.dart` and replace it with:

```dart
import 'package:flutter/material.dart';
import 'screens/splash_screen.dart';

void main() {
  runApp(const BloodReportApp());
}

class BloodReportApp extends StatelessWidget {
  const BloodReportApp({super.key});

  @override
  Widget build(BuildContext context) {
    return MaterialApp(
      debugShowCheckedModeBanner: false,
      title: 'Blood Report Analyzer',
      theme: ThemeData(
        colorScheme: ColorScheme.fromSeed(
          seedColor: Colors.red,
        ),
      ),
      home: const SplashScreen(),
    );
  }
}
```

Notice that `main.dart` is now much smaller. Its job is only to start the app.

